# strategies/

Drop `.qkt` files in this directory. They're mounted into the running daemon at
`/strategies` (read-only). Deploy with `make deploy STRAT=<name>`.

This is the **minimal** template — no broker configured. Strategies run
paper-only. Add a broker to `qkt.config.yaml` + `docker-compose.yml` when ready
to go live.

Scaffolded by qkt v{{QKT_VERSION}}.
